Early-Modern Arts and Sciences'', Brill: Leiden *Jardine, Nicholas, and Wilson, L. eds (2013) ''Recent Material Heritage of the Sciences'', part special issue of ''Studies in History and Philosophy of Science'' 44/4 *Jardine, Nicholas, Granada, M.A, and Mosley, A. (2014) ''Christoph Rothmann's'' Treatise on the Comet'' of 1585: An Edition and Translation with Accompanying Essays'', Brill: Leiden
